Does that put you in danger?

1522
01:39:29,360 --> 01:39:32,520
I get it. But one day
the truth will come out.

1523
01:39:33,000 --> 01:39:35,600
I think your father's gonna
bring everything to light.

1524
01:39:35,680 --> 01:39:38,480
He's an inspiration for so, so many of us.

1525
01:39:39,360 --> 01:39:40,600
Tell him I said that.

1526
01:39:43,360 --> 01:39:44,440
So cool.

